<p>The online influencer looked typically chic as she highlighted her curves in a cream ribbed maxi dress, complete with a thigh-high slit.</p>

<p>Opting for comfort, Malin strolled along in a pair of cosy sandals before switching into a more glamorous outfit for her shoot.</p>

<p>The mental health campaigner was camera-ready when it came to her hair and make-up, as she styled her shoulder-length tresses in bouncy waves and complemented her beauty with a neutral-toned palette.</p>

<p>A dainty gold necklace, a light anklet and aviator shades rounded off the reality star's appearance. </p>

